<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:18:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>研究发现昼夜节律会导致脂肪细胞代谢功能障碍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/circadian-rhythm-drives-metabolic-dysfunction-in-fat-cells-study-finds</link><description>根据《自然代谢》最近发表的一项研究，由查尔斯·F·凯特琳内分泌学和代谢学教授、糖尿病和代谢中心主任约瑟夫·巴斯博士领导的西北医学科学家发现了昼夜节律的破坏如何损害脂肪细胞的代谢功能，为导致肥胖和代谢疾病的分子机制提供了新的见解。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/circadian-rhythm-drives-metabolic-dysfunction-in-fat-cells-study-finds.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:18:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/circadian-rhythm-drives-metabolic-dysfunction-in-fat-cells-study-finds</guid></item><item><title>对新兴第 18 次可持续发展目标阐述的看法——外空委法律小组委员会的一场斯里边活动</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/perspectives-on-an-emerging-18th-sdg-articulation-an-sri-side-event-at-copuos-legal-subcommittee</link><description>SRI 将于 2026 年 4 月 16 日在外空委法律小组委员会期间在 UNOOSA（维也纳）组织一次由 Gülin Dede 博士提议和召集的高级别会外活动，题为&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/perspectives-on-an-emerging-18th-sdg-articulation-an-sri-side-event-at-copuos-legal-subcommittee2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/perspectives-on-an-emerging-18th-sdg-articulation-an-sri-side-event-at-copuos-legal-subcommittee</guid></item><item><title>揭示小鼠中 MERS-CoV 特异性 T 细胞的表位库和保护作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unveiling-the-epitope-repertoires-and-protective-roles-of-mers-cov-specific-t-cells-in-mice</link><description>庄振等.鉴定 C57BL/6 和 BALB/c 小鼠中的 MERS-CoV 特异性 T 细胞表位库，并证明 ORF4b208 特异性 CD4+ 和 ORF5167 特异性 CD8+ T 细胞是多功能效应细胞，对 MERS-CoV 感染具有保护作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/unveiling-the-epitope-repertoires-and-protective-roles-of-mers-cov-specific-t-cells-in-mice2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 00:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unveiling-the-epitope-repertoires-and-protective-roles-of-mers-cov-specific-t-cells-in-mice</guid></item><item><title>研究发现，简单的大脑训练可以降低几十年后患痴呆症的风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/simple-brain-training-cuts-dementia-risk-decades-later-study-finds</link><description>20 年来，老年人的处理速度认知训练显着降低了痴呆风险，其表现优于记忆和推理训练。它的适应性、隐性学习方法可以解释其好处。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/simple-brain-training-cuts-dementia-risk-decades-later-study-finds.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 00:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/simple-brain-training-cuts-dementia-risk-decades-later-study-finds</guid></item><item><title>简单的注射可以帮助心脏病发作后心脏自愈</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-simple-injection-could-help-the-heart-heal-itself-after-a-heart-attack</link><description>一种新的基于 RNA 的疗法旨在解决心脏病学最持久的挑战之一：心脏受伤后无法再生。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-simple-injection-could-help-the-heart-heal-itself-after-a-heart-attack.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 00:18:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-simple-injection-could-help-the-heart-heal-itself-after-a-heart-attack</guid></item><item><title>七个亚群，两种命运：小鼠 γδ T 细胞在癌症免疫中的作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/seven-subsets-two-fates-mouse-%ce%b3%ce%b4-t-cells-in-cancer-immunity</link><description>小鼠 γδ T 细胞在癌症免疫中的作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/seven-subsets-two-fates-mouse-ceb3ceb4-t-cells-in-cancer-immunity2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 00:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/seven-subsets-two-fates-mouse-%ce%b3%ce%b4-t-cells-in-cancer-immunity</guid></item><item><title>人脑的运作接近临界点，但并未达到临界点</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/human-brain-operates-near-but-not-at-the-critical-point</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 23:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/human-brain-operates-near-but-not-at-the-critical-point</guid></item><item><title>新型碳纳米管涂层可以增强 6G 技术</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-carbon-nanotube-coating-could-supercharge-6g-technology</link><description>超薄纳米管薄膜吸收太赫兹波，提高 6G 性能并实现先进的屏蔽和医疗应用。 Skoltech 的研究人员与瑞典 KTH 皇家理工学院的同事合作，开发出了一项可以支持未来 6G 通信的关键技术。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-carbon-nanotube-coating-could-supercharge-6g-technology2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 23:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-carbon-nanotube-coating-could-supercharge-6g-technology</guid></item><item><title>人类真的可以离开地球吗？ 【星际飞船】</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-humans-really-leave-earth-interstellar-spaceship</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 12:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-humans-really-leave-earth-interstellar-spaceship</guid></item><item><title>PI3K 亚型在 PTEN 缺陷的胶质母细胞瘤中的不同作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/divergent-roles-of-pi3k-isoforms-in-pten-deficient-glioblastomas</link><description>（细胞报告&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/divergent-roles-of-pi3k-isoforms-in-pten-deficient-glioblastomas2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 12:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/divergent-roles-of-pi3k-isoforms-in-pten-deficient-glioblastomas</guid></item></channel></rss>